Method Detail

getConfigurations

ReplicationConfigurations getConfigurations(TypeScope scope,
                                            boolean isThisSiteMaster)
                                            throws DimensionsRuntimeException
Returns the list of replication configurations for which this site is either the master or a subordinate.

Parameters:
scope - the type of configurations to include in the collection. Currently, only item and baseline configurations are supported.
isThisSiteMaster - specifies whether to return the list of configurations for which this site is the master or a subordinate. Configurations for which this site is the master are local to this site, while configurations for which this site is a subordinate are remote to this site.
Returns:
the collection of registered replication configurations.
Throws:
DimensionsRuntimeException - if the user has not logged in.
